487
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:57,390
Thomas and I...

488
00:32:58,480 --> 00:33:01,840
<i>We got married two months after your father passed away.</i>

489
00:33:01,840 --> 00:33:05,830
Uh-huh. You understand, we didn't want 
you to think we were disrespecting

490
00:33:05,830 --> 00:33:07,840
the memory of your father.

491
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:14,880
