540
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:04,480
He already has a compromised immune system.

541
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:07,470
He's right. This sample from his eyes is crawling with it.

542
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:09,340
Treat with amphotericin b.

