614
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:29,750
See, you're more me than you pretend. You had to know for sure.

615
00:42:29,750 --> 00:42:31,680
So you needed proof.

616
00:42:33,310 --> 00:42:35,430
The fact that you haven't told me

617
00:42:35,430 --> 00:42:37,250
